text: Jeff Stuebing (born 27 March 1959) is a Canadian former wrestler, born in Hamilton, Ontario, who competed in the 1984 Summer Olympics. In the 1983 Pan American Games 74.0 kg. Greco-Roman category he won the gold medal. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Hamilton, Ontario Category:Olympic wrestlers of Canada Category:Wrestlers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Canadian male sport wrestlers Category:Pan American Games gold medalists for Canada Category:Pan American Games medalists in wrestling Category:Wrestlers at the 1983 Pan American Games
